---
title: Red Thai Style Prawn Coconut Udon Soup with Pak Choi and Mushrooms
description: Red chillies give Thai Red its signature colour, as well as its flavour and heat! Here, our Red Thai Style Prawn Coconut Udon Soup is loaded with veg and thick udon noodles in a curried coconut milk base.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R23_W37_UK_V20250-9_Main_low_2-4bdcaca0.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/668fb0dfda99f37bb7c09034-en-GB.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/red-thai-style-prawn-coconut-udon-soup-668fb0dfda99f37bb7c09034
time required: 35 minutes
course: main course
